---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Now — Stefan Coburn" description="What Stefan Coburn is focused on right now." ogImage="/og/now.png" active="now">
  <main class="container">
    <div class="page-title">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow">/now</div>
        <h1>What I'm<br><em>doing now.</em></h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="now-meta">Last updated March 2026 · inspired by <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener">the /now page movement</a></p>

    <div class="now-body">
      <p>Living in Indiana with my wife Alyssa and our family. She's working through her accelerated nursing program at Purdue, and I'm the stay-at-home dad keeping things running on the home front.</p>
      <p>Volunteering with the local fire department as an EMT and firefighter. Still learning, still showing up.</p>
      <p>Rebuilding this website from WordPress to a static site stack (Astro + Vercel), with the goal of writing more — essays on technology, society, and whatever else is on my mind.</p>
      <p>Practicing piano. Beginner level, but consistent.</p>
      <p>Reading widely and taking notes on what I read. Current shelf is a mix of history, strategy, and human behavior.</p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
